About the creator:
Christian Büffel (LeBueff) is a painter, draftsman, and digital-, analog- working graphic artist, living in Germany, whose works explore the human condition.
In addition, his unmistakable surrealist and abstract compositions take a clear political stance. Büffel creates in a "wild, direct and impulsive" style that includes various digital and analog artistic techniques.
